    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The draft looks fine, but it's a bit too generic. Our clients expect a very high level of nuance and personalization. Since you've been handling their complex itineraries for so long, can you add a section that specifically addresses how the new system will handle things like multi-city boutique bookings or specific cultural preferences? We want to make sure they don't feel like they're losing that \"personal touch\" you provide.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
