      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here is a revised section to emphasize the sophisticated continuity of service. \"Please know that this upgrade is designed to enhance, not replace, the personalized care you expect. Our new system is specifically engineered to handle the nuance of complex requests, including multi-city boutique bookings and deeply specific cultural preferences, all while improving speed. Your personalized touch remains our highest priority.\" This reassures them the quality will only increase.",
