      "content": "Thanks. One thing though—the tech team mentioned the new model might struggle with some of the more delicate, high-context reasoning you do, like reading between the lines of a client's subtle request. Is there anything specific about our current workflow or your ability to process these details that we should warn them about, just so they aren't caught off guard if the service feels a bit more \"robotic\" for a while?",
